#

Classic American Apple Pie

$15
320 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Tags:

DessertBakingClassic

Description

A warm, spiced apple filling encased in a flaky, buttery crust.

Ingredients

  • Granny Smith apples: 6 cups, peeled and sliced
  • Granulated sugar: 3/4 cup
  • Brown sugar: 1/4 cup
  • Ground cinnamon: 2 tsp
  • Nutmeg: 1/4 tsp
  • Lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • Butter: 2 tbsp, cut into small pieces
  • All-purpose flour: 2 1/2 cups
  • Salt: 1/2 tsp
  • Unsalted butter: 1 cup, chilled and diced
  • Ice water: 6-8 tbsp
  • Egg (for egg wash): 1
